To compile link make.inc to the appropriate file for your compiler.
Be sure correct modules are loaded. Example helper scripts 
(make_k.sh make_pfe.sh) do this for the k and pleiades clusters.

Recommend using Intel MKL libraries, but can also download and compile lapack as follows:
wget https://github.com/Reference-LAPACK/lapack/archive/refs/tags/v3.12.1.tar.gz
tar -xvf v3.12.1.tar.gz
cd lapack-3.12.1
cp make.inc.example make.inc
make

Then add 
LDFLAGS = /your/path/here/liblapack.a /your/path/here/librefblas.a
to your make.inc
